      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The committee consisting of\nMessrs. Lang, Brown and Bogard of\nthe trades council has visited the Gas\ncompany in regard to settling the\nstrike. but came to no understanding.\nAt the regular meeting Tuesday eve\nming the committees report was re-\nceived and the committee was dis\ncharged. Instructions were given to\nGasmakers and Yardmen.s union, No.\n269, to continue tho strike."
